<P ID="43"><RG>So</RG>, <NG>you</NG><VG>'re</VG> <NG>a pro-<HEAD>choice</HEAD></NG> <NG>Christian</NG>, <VG>are</VG> <NG>you</NG>? <NG>That</NG> <VG>means</VG> <NG>you</NG><VG>'re</VG> <NG>a <HEAD>hypocrite</HEAD></NG>, <RG>too</RG>. <RG>Here</RG>'s why?
