<P ID="56"><NG>I</NG> <VG>want</VG> <VG-INF>to especially thank</VG-INF> <NG>the helping <HEAD>hands</HEAD></NG> that <VG>were</VG> <NG>my <HEAD>angels</HEAD></NG> <PG>for</PG> <NG>the <HEAD>planting</HEAD></NG> <PG>on</PG> <NG><HEAD>Oct. 16</HEAD></NG>. <NG>The <HEAD>angels</HEAD></NG> <VG>were</VG> <NG><HEAD>Jennie Angel</HEAD></NG>, <NG><HEAD>Valentin Arriaga</HEAD></NG> and <NG><HEAD>Alice Chopper</HEAD></NG>. <PG>Without</PG> <NG>your <HEAD>help</HEAD></NG> <NG>I</NG> <VG>would have been</VG> <NG>all <HEAD>weekend</HEAD></NG> <VG-VBG>getting</VG-VBG> <NG>it</NG> <VG>done</VG>. <NG>I</NG> <VG>can't thank</VG> <NG>you</NG> <PG>enough for</PG> <NG>your <HEAD>help</HEAD></NG>.
